From: Jordan Feldstein <jfeldstein@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 11 Apr 2026 08:47:48 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] feat(cfha): LangChain supervisor + subagent tools on trigger

- Remove TriggerBody.subagent; add message; reject legacy subagent with 400
- Supervisor via langchain.agents.create_agent; subagents as LangGraph subgraph tools
- Split subagent execution (subagent_exec), MCP/skill steps (trigger_steps)
- Helm: chatModel -> HOSTED_AGENT_CHAT_MODEL; schema description/exposeAsTool
- README + observability docs; tests use fake chat model for tool routing
